(49, '<pre>Which one of the following is correct about the statements given below?\n  All function calls are resolved at compile-time in Procedure Oriented Programming.\n  All function calls are resolved at compile-time in OOPS.\n</pre>', '<pre>Only II is correct.</pre>', '<pre>Both I and II are correct.</pre>', '<pre>Only I is correct.</pre>', '<pre>Both I and II are incorrect.</pre>', 'C'),
