('LT Infotech', 'L&T Infotech is a global IT services and solutions provider. We provide the winning edge to our clients by leveraging our Business-to-IT Connect and deeply committed people. Our clients include industry leaders like Chevron, Freescale, Hitachi, Sanyo and Lafarge, among others.', 'l&t infotech.jpg'),
