(197, '<pre>\n\n		\n		<p>// we are given the root of a tree and a leaf</p>\n<p>// now the leaf becomes the root node and rest of the tree is attracted down due to gravity</p>\n<p>//                       for example  for tree</p>\n<p></p>\n<pre>//                                                        1<br />\n//                                        2                                           3<br />\n//                                4            5                          6                            7<br />\n//                            8      9  10   11<br />\n<br />\n//   let us call converttree(1,10)  10 is the passed leaf node<br />\n//    now after the funtion call tree would be<br />\n//                                      10<br />\n5<br />\n2                 11<br />\n4        1<br />\n8   9        3<br />\n6    7</pre>\n<p></p>\n\n		\n	</pre>', 'Leaf as the Root.. Walmart interview question', 'walmart.jpg'),
