(207, '<pre>\n\n		\n		<p>Consider the given structure:</p>\n<p></p>\n<pre><br />\nstruct node<br />\n{<br />\nint data;<br />\nstruct node *next;<br />\nstruct node *next_larger;<br />\n}</pre>\n<p></p>\n<p>You are given a list where each node is of type defined above. Initially all the next larger pointer of each node points to NULL. Write an algorithm to update the next larger pointer of each so that they point to immediate next largest node in the list.</p>\n<p>e.g.</p>\n<p></p>\n<pre><br />\n4\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;8\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;2\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;1\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;9<br />\n|-&gt;NULL   |-&gt;NULL  |-&gt;NULL  |-&gt;NULL  |-&gt;NULL<br />\n<br />\nOutput:<br />\n|\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n|<br />\nV              |\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n!\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\nV<br />\n4\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;8\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;2\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;1\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n&gt;9<br />\n|\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n^               ^\n<hr class="bbcode_rule" />\n|               |---&gt;NULL<br />\n</pre>\n<p></p>\n\n		\n	</pre>', 'Adobe Interview Question for Software Engineer/Developer about Linked Lists', 'adobe.jpg'),
