(377, '<pre>\n\n		\n		<p>write a program which relplaces some particular string with some other. like if we have to change bad with good then &#8220;he is a bad boy will change to he is a good boy&#8221; but if we have something like &#8220;hyderabad is bad&#8221;, then it has to be changed to &#8220;hyderabad is good&#8221; (not to change bad in hyderabad to good)\n</p>\n<p></p>\n\n		\n	</pre>', 'Oracle Interview Question for Software Engineer/Developer (Fresher) about Strings', 'oracle.jpg'),
